      "transform": "switch_v13_middle_dot_to_center_dot"
    },
    {
      "id": 8249,
      "ko": "\u001bCC고마키야마\u001bCZ에서 대치한 \u001bCA[bs754]히데요시\u001bCZ군과\n\u001bCA오다 노부카쓰\u001bCZ·\u001bCA[b1871]\u001bCZ의 연합군―",
      "planned_ko_utf16le_sha256": "B3576154ADA0691CA4B6DD0CA713EBE900F77D55A59D9D3497536791BD554389",
